{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Build a Shopify OS 2.0 custom section called “Stories of Transformation – Testimonial Slider”.
    
    Design:
    - Same dark background + centered serif heading.
    - Desktop: show 3 cards in a row.
    - Mobile: transform into a horizontal swipe slider with snap points and dots (pagination).
    
    Card styling:
    - Dark card background, thin border, gold stars, quote, avatar + name + sub-label.
    
    Animation (animate everything, different style):
    - Header appears first (fade + slight rise).
    - Cards enter as a horizontal glide:
      - Card 1 slides in from left, Card 2 from bottom, Card 3 from right (subtle, not dramatic).
      - Stagger timing 120ms.
    - Stars “fill” animation: stars scale up slightly as they appear (no twinkle, more modern).
    - On mobile slider:
      - When a card becomes active (centered), it gains a stronger shadow and slightly higher opacity.
      - Inactive cards are slightly dimmed.
    
    Hover (desktop):
    - “Magnetic” hover feel: card tilts 1 degree toward cursor (very subtle) + border glow increases slightly.
    - Disable tilt on mobile.
    
    Technical:
    - Use IntersectionObserver for entrance.
    - Use CSS scroll-snap for slider (no JS slider libraries).
    - prefers-reduced-motion disables slides/tilt; keeps snap.
    , can you make this more minimal vibe. matte nude color 
{% enddoc %}
